00:14:25,360 --> 00:14:27,200
Let me take you somewhere first.

162
00:14:27,200 --> 00:14:31,220
Sophie Carver. A famous woman photographer who herself is handicapped.

163
00:14:31,220 --> 00:14:35,080
She's been shooting people with rare diseases around the globe.

164
00:14:35,080 --> 00:14:42,440
I saw on Photoworld that she's holding an exhibition in Prague, so I invited her to hold one in China.

165
00:14:42,440 --> 00:14:49,100
I hope these photos can encourage patients with HD to raise hope for life again.

166
00:14:55,400 --> 00:15:00,740
The purpose of us holding this exhibition is to call on society to pay attention to people with rare diseases.

167
00:15:00,740 --> 00:15:06,060
